HowTo markup WormBook chapters in DocBook XML with links to WormBase.

 shell> ./WormbaseLinkGenerator.pl --def_file WormbaseLinks.def \
                                   --locus_url http://www.sanger.ac.uk/Projects/C_elegans/LOCI/loci_all.txt \
                                   --wormbase_aceserver aceserver.cshl.org \
				   --input_files docbook.xml

   For any given release, the first time the script is run it will create a reference directory
   for that release, eg WS210/. This directory will be several GB in size.

   Subsequent invocations for the provided release will rely on this directory at
   significant time savings.  Invoke as:

 shell> ./WormBaseLinkGenerator.pl --link_directory WS210/ \ 
 	                           --input_files docbook2.xml




	Todd Harris
